metadata.bio: leejean (리진) is a South Korean singer-songwriter under Media Asia Korea. She made her solo debut on March 3, 2023 with her first English digital single "Old School Love". In 2023 and 2024, she competed as Sing Again 3 Singer No.68 (싱어게인3 68호 가수) on the JTBC survival show Sing Again 3 and finished in fifth place.
